                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A songtwisted is able to bend its body in unusual ways, gaining a +6 racial bonus to Acrobatics checks to escape. However, any time a songtwisted isn\u2019t focusing on their movement, their limbs twist in unnatural arrangements on their own. Another creature can notice the effort required to keep the twisting in check with a successful Sense Motive check (DC = 10 + the songtwisted\u2019s Bluff modifier).",
